<para>
GCombust is an interface to cd burning, it can burn data on the fly
from hard drive, without making an image, cd-to-cd data copy on the
fly. Supports easy creation of ISO images and audio cd creation (audio
to WAV, WAV to audio, audio cd direct copy). It can burn in
multisession mode and bootable cd as well.
</para>
